title: A Degree of Faith: A Case for Christianity for the Skeptic
description:
A Degree of Faith: A Case for Christianity for the Educated Skeptic -  Joel Mabry  epub/mobi

"A Degree of Faith" addresses serious objections to Christianity in an in-depth, concise, and entertaining manner. It does not shy away from objections to faith or set up logical "strawmen" to destroy, but faces objections to Christianity head-on with stringent logic and thorough research.
